reviewText: This type of video is usually given away free to promote the products.  I can't believe I bought it.  The problem I bought 2 other tapes by this same company and they are thesam.. Shame, Shame on me!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!
In this video you will see them develop the plug design, construct the plug from scratch and build the large polyester mold all in an environment similar to a home garage!
